    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
}
```

#### Input Field Pattern
```css
.auth-input {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    width: 100%;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-card);       /* Subtle border */
    background: var(--bg-primary);              /* Cream background */
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    box-sizing: border-box;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
}

.auth-input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--accent-amber);          /* Gold focus border */
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.12);  /* Gold glow */
    background: var(--bg-primary);
}
```

#### Form Card Pattern
```css
.auth-form-card {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 400px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 28px;
    background: var(--bg-card);                 /* Nearly white card */
    border: 1px solid var(--border-card);       /* Subtle border */
